							<div id="post-63330" class="post post-63330 type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-budget category-education category-race-society category-reporting category-tip-sheets tag-american-educational-research-association tag-famu tag-florida-am-university tag-florida-classic tag-google-scholar tag-hazing tag-hbcus tag-historically-black-colleges-and-universities tag-investigative-journalism tag-marching-band tag-open-access-institutions tag-robert-champion tag-solutions-journalism-network">
