							<!-- Start Title -->
							<h1 class="title single-title">Covering minority communities: Lessons I learned from my HBCU investigation</h1>
							&nbsp;
							<!-- End Title -->
							<!-- Begin Image -->
							 
								<div class="single-thumb">
									<img width="720" height="480" src="https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/FAMU-marching-band-720x480.jpg" class="attachment-bgthumb size-bgthumb wp-post-image" alt="HBCU historically black college FAMU Pulitzer Denise-Marie Ordway" title="" srcset="https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/FAMU-marching-band-720x480.jpg 720w, https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/FAMU-marching-band-300x200.jpg 300w, https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/FAMU-marching-band-768x513.jpg 768w, https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/FAMU-marching-band-353x235.jpg 353w, https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/FAMU-marching-band-220x147.jpg 220w, https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/FAMU-marching-band.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 720px) 100vw, 720px" />									<div class="caption">Florida A&M University marching band, 2014. (U.S. Army/Sgt. John L. Carkeet IV)</div>
																	</div>
														<!-- End Image -->
						</header>
						<!-- author and social begin -->
						<div class="floatright">
							<div class="floatleft"><div class="a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_22 addtoany_list" data-a2a-url="https://journalistsresource.org/tip-sheets/reporting/covering-minority-communities-hbcu/" data-a2a-title="Covering minority communities: Lessons I learned from my HBCU investigation"><a class="a2a_button_facebook" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/facebook?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjournalistsresource.org%2Ftip-sheets%2Freporting%2Fcovering-minority-communities-hbcu%2F&amp;linkname=Covering%20minority%20communities%3A%20Lessons%20I%20learned%20from%20my%20HBCU%20investigation" title="Facebook" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-wpel-link="external"></a><a class="a2a_button_twitter" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/twitter?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjournalistsresource.org%2Ftip-sheets%2Freporting%2Fcovering-minority-communities-hbcu%2F&amp;linkname=Covering%20minority%20communities%3A%20Lessons%20I%20learned%20from%20my%20HBCU%20investigation" title="Twitter" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-wpel-link="external"></a><a class="a2a_button_linkedin" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/linkedin?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjournalistsresource.org%2Ftip-sheets%2Freporting%2Fcovering-minority-communities-hbcu%2F&amp;linkname=Covering%20minority%20communities%3A%20Lessons%20I%20learned%20from%20my%20HBCU%20investigation" title="LinkedIn" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-wpel-link="external"></a><a class="a2a_button_reddit" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/reddit?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjournalistsresource.org%2Ftip-sheets%2Freporting%2Fcovering-minority-communities-hbcu%2F&amp;linkname=Covering%20minority%20communities%3A%20Lessons%20I%20learned%20from%20my%20HBCU%20investigation" title="Reddit" rel="nofollow noopener" target="_blank" data-wpel-link="external"></a><a class="a2a_button_email" href="https://www.addtoany.com/add_to/email?linkurl=https%3A%2F%2Fjournalistsresource.org%2Ftip-sheets%2Freporting%2Fcovering-minority-communities-hbcu%2F&amp;