																								<li class="cat-post-item">
									<a rel="nofollow" class="cat-post-thumbnail  cat-post-none" href="https://journalistsresource.org/tip-sheets/reporting/news-collaboration-model-legislation/" rel="bookmark" title="How they did it: News collaboration exposes how special interests use ‘model&#8217; legislation">
										<span class="rthumb">
																							<img width="75" height="75" src="https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/model-bill-2-75x75.jpg" class="attachment-sidethumb size-sidethumb wp-post-image" alt="" title="" srcset="https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/model-bill-2-75x75.jpg 75w, https://journalistsresource.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/model-bill-2-150x150.jpg 150w" sizes="(max-width: 75px) 100vw, 75px" />																					</span>
										<span>How they did it: News collaboration exposes how special interests use ‘model&#8217; legislation</span>
									</a>
								</li>
																								<li class="cat-post-item">
